channel.title: C# RSC Server (Project Untitled) Source Release
channel.description:
Bakatool was too lazy to put this up, full credits to him this was entirely his.
Its made from scratch completely in C# and requires
Microsoft Visual C# 2005 Express Microsoft SQL Server 2005
and any 202 client.
[b]NO HELP WILL BE PROVIDED SETTING THIS UP IN ANY WAY[/b] This server was made over 8 months ago, and i belive was the best server around then (just unreleased)
Features (if i can remember)
~Full Herblaw ~Full Fletching ~Full Mining ~Full Fishing ~Full Prayer ~Full Woodcutting ~Full combat, full magic and partial ranged.
It had quite alot of bugs in it.
Download link: http://uppit.com/WD2XU6
Agian [b]NO HELP WILL BE PROVIDED SETTING THIS UP IN ANY WAY. [/b]
